snippet.title: Divinity 2: The Dragon Knight Saga Trailer
snippet.description:
The demo for Divinity 2: The Dragon Knight Saga launches today on Xbox Live. Celebrate with the official trailer for the new RPG.

IGN's YouTube is just a taste of our content. Get more:
